storing some value for me.

00:10:44.690 --> 00:10:47.470
It's got a serial number.

00:10:47.470 --> 00:10:50.380
That piece of paper itself
is not the store of value,

00:10:50.380 --> 00:10:53.260
in a sense, even
though we accept it.

00:10:53.260 --> 00:10:55.870
Would you say that's
a store of value?

00:10:55.870 --> 00:10:57.940
AUDIENCE: In some ways.

00:10:57.940 --> 00:11:00.460
