was a South American drug lord

00:25:02.980 --> 00:25:07.640
family, this drug lord was
on the verge of being caught.

00:25:07.640 --> 00:25:12.300
All their assets were being
seized by the government.

00:25:12.300 --> 00:25:16.100
And the story is told by
