00:50:48.450 --> 00:50:48.950
network?

00:50:48.950 --> 00:50:50.120
Which one did they do?

00:50:50.120 --> 00:50:52.550
ROBLEH ALI: I think it
was, they just claimed

00:50:52.550 --> 00:50:53.690
Etherium and deployed it.

00:50:53.690 --> 00:50:56.290
Like internet-- it wasn't
ever outside the [INAUDIBLE]..

00:50:56.290 --> 00:50:57.830
AUDIENCE: They
were doing mining?

00:50:57.830 --> 00:50:59.538
ROBLEH ALI: I don't
know how they did it,

00:50:59.538 --> 00:51:01.040
in terms of mechanism.

00:51:01.040 --> 00:51:02.540
GARY GENSLER: Now,
what you'll see--

00:51:02.540 --> 00:51:06.180
because I want to
quickly go to phase two.

00:51:06.180 --> 00:51:09.960
Phase two, none of
them used Ethereum.

00:51:09.960 --> 00:51:12.900
Phase two, two more
initiatives happened--

00:51:12.900 --> 00:51:14.290
Japan and Europe together.

00:51:14.290 --> 00:51:16.890
And when I say Japan and Europe,
